quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,43,"Ma tasbiqu min ommatin ajalahawama yasta/khiroon"
  23,44,"Thumma arsalna rusulana tatrakulla ma jaa ommatan rasooluha kaththaboohufaatbaAAna baAAdahum baAAdan wajaAAalnahumahadeetha fabuAAdan liqawmin la yu/minoon"
  23,45,"Thumma arsalna moosa waakhahuharoona bi-ayatina wasultaninmubeen"
  23,46,"Ila firAAawna wamala-ihi fastakbaroowakanoo qawman AAaleen"
  23,47,"Faqaloo anu/minu libasharayni mithlinawaqawmuhuma lana AAabidoon"
  23,48,"Fakaththaboohuma fakanoomina almuhlakeen"
  23,49,"Walaqad atayna moosaalkitaba laAAallahum yahtadoon"
  23,50,"WajaAAalna ibna maryama waommahu ayatanwaawaynahuma ila rabwatin thatiqararin wamaAAeen"
  23,51,"Ya ayyuha arrusulukuloo mina attayyibati waAAmaloo salihaninnee bima taAAmaloona AAaleem"
  23,52,"Wa-inna hathihi ommatukum ommatan wahidatanwaana rabbukum fattaqoon"
  23,53,"FataqattaAAoo amrahum baynahumzuburan kullu hizbin bima ladayhim farihoon"
  23,54,"Fatharhum fee ghamratihim hattaheen"
  23,55,"Ayahsaboona annama numidduhumbihi min malin wabaneen"
  23,56,"NusariAAu lahum fee alkhayratibal la yashAAuroon"
  23,57,"Inna allatheena hum min khashyatirabbihim mushfiqoon"
  23,58,"Wallatheena hum bi-ayatirabbihim yu/minoon"
  23,59,"Wallatheena hum birabbihim layushrikoon"
